{"tid":407364,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"癡撚線公司!!!!!!《出貓特攻隊》女神Oomeisaya本周四襲港!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!","createTime":"2017-09-20T11:24:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-21T05:25:49.000Z","uid":9573,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ac8f41ff2995d5b925cb1f2dca777ea50cfd58c4","tid":407364,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T11:24:19.000Z","msg":"泰國校園賣座片《出貓特攻隊》在港同樣熱爆，早前三位主角Non，Aokbab及James來港宣傳，日前就輪到另一位女神級主角依莎亞賀素雲（Oomeisaya，簡稱Oom）襲港！被封為「泰國朱千雪」的Oom清秀甜美，今個星期四首度來港，與「正版」朱千雪同場出席「星展銀行Live More SnapTag」發布會！究竟邊位女神受歡迎啲呢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/uDmp3LUuRDIPWwh9TrnMCw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/orientalsundayent.com/c58ebea96e8f6e52437091ddae941744\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FuDmp3LUuRDIPWwh9TrnMCw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Forientalsundayent.com%2Fc58ebea96e8f6e52437091ddae941744&h=d9991044&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「泰國朱千雪」Oomeisaya本周四襲港<br />\n<br />\n本周四舉行的「星展銀行 Live More SnapTag」發布會，邀請了人氣爆燈的朱千雪 ，以及被譽為「全泰國最清新女孩 」的Oomeisaya 作主禮嘉賓。活動中千雪會接受考驗智慧的挑戰，正修讀藝術的Oom則會大秀精湛畫技，兩位仙氣女神更會交流大談活出精彩Live More的秘訣。千雪及Oom一對港、泰女神會進行「世紀自拍」，成為「星展銀行 Live More SnapTag」首批參加者，邀請全城參與贏取每週大獎。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Up7kqdDJ7CbRHo.qoBLvcw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/orientalsundayent.com/b98e64103601d64ece1f605728f61616\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FUp7kqdDJ7CbRHo.qoBLvcw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Forientalsundayent.com%2Fb98e64103601d64ece1f605728f61616&h=4cd47ad8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《出貓特攻隊》女神Oom<br />\n<br />\nOomeisaya在熱爆電影《出貓特攻隊》中飾演「明詩」，為電影第二女主角，片中佢係天才女主角「超蓮」的朋友，成績差的Oom不時都系楚楚可憐的樣子，成功打動女主角幫佢出貓。Oom在現實中係校花，電影中同樣出眾梁烈唯大馬開工遭走數：仲用緊我個名招搖，校服造型極清秀甜美，深深吸引觀眾眼球！<br />\n仙氣校花<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ONqw3kWssE5KfkbGK_wGEw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/orientalsundayent.com/047deb21440c322443f979b01d26c6f6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FONqw3kWssE5KfkbGK_wGEw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Forientalsundayent.com%2F047deb21440c322443f979b01d26c6f6&h=895d7053&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1996年出生的Oom芳齡21歲，有着濃密的眉毛和深邃的眼眸，眼大大笑容非常甜美，散發陣陣仙氣，略施脂粉已經睇到男士們目不轉睛！2014年時，當時只有15歲的Oom憑出眾的外表被星探發掘，自此從事模特兒工作，目前就讀於藝術學院裝飾藝術科系。"},{"pid":"0a70c635bd478c7301268c6d9b98535c2a2552db","tid":407364,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T12:03:00.000Z","msg":"oom!!!"},{"pid":"802c8aab504cee99f735c7b70855ba7e6032a06b","tid":407364,"uid":34686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T00:18:13.000Z","msg":"靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a57b0da9c7a26337cf71946dffab5f1764bc4d6d","tid":407364,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T00:29:27.000Z","msg":"睇唔到圖既"},{"pid":"714d0359eccd94fc98649834460a6c84c57effc2","tid":407364,"uid":16172,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T01:48:24.000Z","msg":"電影中同樣出眾梁烈唯大馬開工遭走數：仲用緊我個名招搖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99c8d04574534043d09750e4e9c0b72253a35a7d","tid":407364,"uid":32151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T02:02:25.000Z","msg":"1996出生 現年21歲 2014時點15歲呀"},{"pid":"5ca9624972e29a816e153d4c9a3fd252bb7cf99a","tid":407364,"uid":66496,"like":0,"dis